# Retail Sales Analytics Dashboard

## Project Overview

This project analyzes Global Superstore sales data and provides business insights using:

- Power BI
- SQL
- Data Analytics
- Data Visualization

## Dashboard Preview

![Global Superstore Dashboard](screenshots/dashboard.png)

## Key Insights

- Sales and Profit analysis
- Category-wise performance
- Regional sales trends
- Customer segment analysis
- Shipping mode analysis

## Tools Used

- Power BI
- MySQL
- Excel/CSV Dataset
- SQL Queries